    <snippet> paṭhamataraṃ kālaṃ kareyyaṃ, anacchariyaṃ kho panetaṃ yaṃ maṃ bhagavā evaṃ byākareyya – ‘natthi taṃ saṃyojanaṃ yena saṃyojanena saṃyutto citto gahapati puna imaṃ lokaṃ āgaccheyyā’’’ti. Evaṃ vutte, acelo kassapo cittaṃ gahapatiṃ etadavoca – acchariyaṃ vata bho, abbhutaṃ vata bho! Dhammassa svākkhātatā, yatra hi nāma gihī odātavasano </snippet>
